{"tid":874352,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Mac book pro late 2013 SSD 升級教學","createTime":"2018-10-24T06:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T16:39:08.000Z","uid":102296,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be287998dc450804f5d158534f5e276f79786dda","tid":874352,"uid":102296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"Mac book pro late 2013 升級教學<br />\n<br />\n坊間很少提供如何升級2013年左右的SSD. 因為當時的SSD並沒有統一的介面標準.  當時跟機的SSD既不是SATA, 也不是NVME, 而是AHCI over PCIe的獨特界面. 而現在流行的NVME M.2 SSD根本並不兼容當時的OS及接頭。如要簡易的換法(如ifixit的做法)只能用舊有蘋果零件更換。或者買專用SSD,效果不理想而且很貴.<br />\n<br />\n自從High Sierra 開始OS X已經能用NMVE開機，但是當年的SSD接頭，需然都是PCIe但不是NVMe的M.2接頭，所以要用一張轉插咭去解決問題.<br />\n<br />\n所以其實升級SSD並不容易。<br />\n<br />\n首先要<br />\n升級OSX至High Sierra或以上，<br />\n然後用time machine備份資料. 舊有SSD要買特別的轉插才能接成外置USB SSD.<br />\n然後拆機, 將新的NVMe SSD插上特製的轉插咭, 再插回主板上，<br />\n然後再灌新OS。<br />\n最後把資料回復。完成升級。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUfSiYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUfSiYc.png&h=efc74d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用最新的os, 先可以支援boot from nvme, high sierra以上 mojave應該冇伏,我呢部2013年用到衣家都仲係好快.<br />\n<br />\nBoot rom: MBP112.0146.B00<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3COc3qd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3COc3qd.png&h=44afb898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n升級前ssd資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q966oqN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ966oqN.png&h=d2233be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物料<br />\n1. NGFF 轉插:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmtTNSC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmtTNSC.png&h=218c29a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. SSD 一隻 (NVME M.2)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/juwBLEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjuwBLEy.png&h=ac78c56b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 螺絲批 Torx 5, Pentahole 5 (1.2mm), 十字頭 <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9gaP6q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9gaP6q.png&h=f048573f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. USB 碟 (16GB 以上), 用黎裝osx. (冇圖)<br />\n<br />\n5. 外置硬碟, 備份用 (冇圖)<br />\n<br />\n步驟1: 接上外置硬碟, 用time machine備份<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh5OBMY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh5OBMY.png&h=f59653f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n備份完要移除外置硬碟.<br />\n<br />\n步驟2: 準備MAC OSX的影像碟<br />\n詳情 <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT201372&d=XtradmV451CgdR%2FzWqTAFzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ae6ca42e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201372</a><br />\n<br />\n2.1 下載 最新 mac osx，選download便好:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XH7mckv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXH7mckv.png&h=aed71702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下載後出現以下畫面, 不用continue<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOXmckV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOXmckV.png&h=6f472236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接上usb碟, 然後到terminal 執行下面命令<br />\nsudo /Applications/Install\\ macOS\\ <a href=\"http://Mojave.app/Contents/Resources/createinstallmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojave.app%2FContents%2FResources%2Fcreateinstallmedia&d=XtradmV451CgdR%2FzWqTAFzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=aba29f35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojave.app/Contents/Resources/createinstallmedia</a> --volume /Volumes/MACOSX<br />\n呢個命令會將usb碟上面的資料全部刪除，所以唔好搞錯左，接左外置硬碟就麻煩<br />\n圖中的MACOSX係我隻usb碟，真正名稱要睇份你個usb drive的volume name<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Spr7Va.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Spr7Va.png&h=c3f90c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n步驟3:拆殻, 用pentalobe螺絲批<br />\n參考資料:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ifixit.com/Guide/MacBook+Pro+13-Inch+Retina+Display+Late+2013+SSD+Replacement/26811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifixit.com%2FGuide%2FMacBook%2BPro%2B13-Inch%2BRetina%2BDisplay%2BLate%2B2013%2BSSD%2BReplacement%2F26811&d=XtradmV451CgdR%2FzWqTAFzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=dd493a3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ifixit.com/Guide/MacBook+Pro+13-Inch+Retina+Display+Late+2013+SSD+Replacement/26811</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Af1J98T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAf1J98T.png&h=318ba2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換ssd: 用Torx 5 螺絲批<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6PzxnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6PzxnF.png&h=ed329cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊SSD<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lx3ksWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLx3ksWB.png&h=d32f57cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新 SSD <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7BdMou6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BdMou6.png&h=d41bf650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尺寸一樣，但係接口完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n插新SSD的情況, 可以見到有一層底的轉插，上面接EVO970 SSD. 記得最後要上螺絲固定位置.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHnhvb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHnhvb6.png&h=d8fab7c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n步驟4: 灌OS安裝過程<br />\n<br />\n安裝完成後上返螺絲，然後插之前整的usb 開機, 然後開disk utility<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHbumg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHbumg2.png&h=32f18e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先去disk utility 格式化ssd, MAC OS已經搵到新SSD, 選新SSD然後erase<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SCGKaaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSCGKaaN.png&h=8bb64547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名可以隨意選 <br />\nFormat 建議選  Mac OS extended (journaled)<br />\nScheme建議選 GUID Partition Map<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MAnGhL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MAnGhL.png&h=cd1dec77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n格式化完成就可以用:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xh2JqKz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxh2JqKz.png&h=11cc0f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後退出disk utility,開始灌OS<br />\n用新裝的SSD灌OS<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzfSi4L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzfSi4L.png&h=bc0b459c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n步驟5: 回復資料<br />\n灌完 OS最後步驟就係用之前的time machine備份去回復資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gVrowA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gVrowA.png&h=7a32fc78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安裝完成後的 system report, 舊SSD 係AHCI, 5.0GT/s x 2 251GB,新SSD係NVMe 5.0GT/s x4 1TB<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZGaQbM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZGaQbM.png&h=03e68738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完成<br />\n<br />\n有乜唔明可以問，但係未心會答."},{"pid":"8ccf07e1240a1d8abad559cf8e5ce9d00f9c08df","tid":874352,"uid":77192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"MBP 13 early 2015 做法係咪一樣"},{"pid":"c6827bcba9d5c5d8b3f56ea0c7851be465f7e944","tid":874352,"uid":102296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccf07e1240a1d8abad559cf8e5ce9d00f9c08df","tid":874352,"uid":77192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"MBP 13 early 2015 做法係咪一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"應該一樣"},{"pid":"5bb5ad7ab9ec32508b97add538f12611aeb1b904","tid":874352,"uid":76419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6827bcba9d5c5d8b3f56ea0c7851be465f7e944","tid":874352,"uid":102296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8